20
00:01:07,359 --> 00:01:08,040
Oh, that's cool.

21
00:01:08,340 --> 00:01:08,900
How's it going?

22
00:01:09,500 --> 00:01:13,920
Well, I'm finding the classes pretty tough actually, but I'm having a great time in Shanghai.

23
00:01:14,120 --> 00:01:15,420
It's really an amazing city.

24
00:01:15,780 --> 00:01:16,540
It sure is.

25
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:17,879
Are you staying for long?

26
00:01:18,379 --> 00:01:19,659
Only two weeks, unfortunately.

27
00:01:20,180 --> 00:01:21,879
I wish I could stay longer, but...

28
00:01:21,879 --> 00:01:25,840
