40
00:01:57,599 --> 00:02:00,040
You hear this phrase, nice to meet you.

41
00:02:00,379 --> 00:02:08,240
Right, so obviously if you meet someone new, you're introduced by your friend or something, you can just say, hi, nice to meet you.

42
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:12,340
All right, so nice to meet you, nice to meet you too.

43
00:02:12,460 --> 00:02:16,780
