137
00:06:26,980 --> 00:06:27,399
It's a thing.

138
00:06:28,279 --> 00:06:31,180
It's like a party, but it's a small party, right?

139
00:06:31,639 --> 00:06:32,660
A little get together.

140
00:06:33,100 --> 00:06:41,399
So I like to think of a get together as something very casual, something very small, sometimes intimate where you just have three or four or five friends.

141
00:06:42,180 --> 00:06:45,759
And it's not as big as a party where everyone is dancing.

142
00:06:46,399 --> 00:06:46,699
Okay.

143
00:06:47,019 --> 00:06:49,980
So a little get together is just a small group of people.

144
00:06:50,100 --> 00:06:53,100
You invite them over to your house, very relaxed, very casual.

145
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:54,500
It's not really a party.

146
00:06:54,500 --> 00:06:56,600
It's more of a reunion of friends.

147
00:06:56,959 --> 00:06:58,000
And like we said, it's a noun.

148
00:06:58,139 --> 00:06:59,980
